The paper discusses a technique for optimizing answer set programming, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The technique involves rewriting rules, which is a common technique in logic programming (cs.PL) and optimization (cs.LO). The paper also mentions the use of circuits (cs.DS) and experiments on benchmark problems (cs.DM).
